var book = {
	"name": "Colossians",
	"numChapters": 4,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29450A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29450A\"></sup>an apostle of Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29450B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29450B\"></sup>by the will of God, and Timothy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29450C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29450C\"></sup>our brother,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29451D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29451D\"></sup>saints and faithful brothers in Christ at Colossae:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29451E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29451E\"></sup>Grace to you and peace from God our Father.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29452F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29452F\"></sup>We always thank God, the Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, when we pray for you,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>since we heard of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29453G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29453G\"></sup>your faith in Christ Jesus and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29453H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29453H\"></sup>the love that you have for all the saints,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29454I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29454I\"></sup>the hope <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29454J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29454J\"></sup>laid up for you in heaven. Of this you have heard before in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29454K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29454K\"></sup>the word of the truth, the gospel,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>which has come to you, as indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29455L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29455L\"></sup>in the whole world it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29455M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29455M\"></sup>bearing fruit and increasing—as it also does among you, since the day you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29455N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29455N\"></sup>heard it and understood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29455O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29455O\"></sup>the grace of God in truth,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>just as you learned it from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29456P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29456P\"></sup>Epaphras our beloved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29456Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29456Q\"></sup>fellow servant. He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29456R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29456R\"></sup>a faithful minister of Christ on your behalf",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and has made known to us your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29457S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29457S\"></sup>love in the Spirit.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And so, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29458T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29458T\"></sup>from the day we heard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29458U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29458U\"></sup>we have not ceased to pray for you, asking that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29458V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29458V\"></sup>you may be filled with the knowledge of his will in all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29458W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29458W\"></sup>spiritual wisdom and understanding,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>so as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29459X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29459X\"></sup>to walk in a manner worthy of the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29459Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29459Y\"></sup>fully pleasing to him: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29459Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29459Z\"></sup>bearing fruit in every good work and increasing in the knowledge of God;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29460AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29460AA\"></sup>being strengthened with all power, according to his glorious might, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29460AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29460AB\"></sup>all endurance and patience <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29460AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29460AC\"></sup>with joy;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29461AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29461AD\"></sup>giving thanks to the Father, who has qualified you to share in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29461AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29461AE\"></sup>the inheritance of the saints in light.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29462AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29462AF\"></sup>has delivered us from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29462AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29462AG\"></sup>the domain of darkness and transferred us to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29462AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29462AH\"></sup>the kingdom of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29462AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29462AI\"></sup>his beloved Son,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29463AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29463AJ\"></sup>in whom we have redemption, the forgiveness of sins.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29464AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29464AK\"></sup>He is the image of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29464AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29464AL\"></sup>the invisible God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29464AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29464AM\"></sup>the firstborn of all creation.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For by him all things were created, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29465AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29465AN\"></sup>in heaven and on earth, visible and invisible, whether <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29465AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29465AO\"></sup>thrones or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29465AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29465AP\"></sup>dominions or rulers or authorities—all things were created <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29465AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29465AQ\"></sup>through him and for him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29466AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29466AR\"></sup>he is before all things, and in him all things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29466AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29466AS\"></sup>hold together.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29467AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29467AT\"></sup>he is the head of the body, the church. He is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29467AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29467AU\"></sup>the beginning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29467AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29467AV\"></sup>the firstborn from the dead, that in everything he might be preeminent.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29468AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29468AW\"></sup>in him all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29468AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29468AX\"></sup>fullness of God was pleased to dwell,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29469AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29469AY\"></sup>through him to reconcile to himself all things, whether on earth or in heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29469AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29469AZ\"></sup>making peace <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29469BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29469BA\"></sup>by the blood of his cross.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29470BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29470BB\"></sup>And you, who once were alienated and hostile in mind, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29470BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29470BC\"></sup>doing evil deeds,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>he has now reconciled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29471BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29471BD\"></sup>in his body of flesh by his death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29471BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29471BE\"></sup>in order to present you holy and blameless and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29471BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29471BF\"></sup>above reproach before him,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29472BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29472BG\"></sup>if indeed you continue in the faith, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29472BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29472BH\"></sup>stable and steadfast, not shifting from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29472BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29472BI\"></sup>the hope of the gospel that you heard, which has been proclaimed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29472BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29472BJ\"></sup>in all creation under heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29472BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29472BK\"></sup>and of which I, Paul, became a minister.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29473BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29473BL\"></sup>I rejoice in my sufferings for your sake, and in my flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29473BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29473BM\"></sup>I am filling up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29473BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29473BN\"></sup>what is lacking in Christ's afflictions <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29473BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29473BO\"></sup>for the sake of his body, that is, the church,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29474BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29474BP\"></sup>of which I became a minister according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29474BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29474BQ\"></sup>the stewardship from God that was given to me for you, to make the word of God fully known,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29475BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29475BR\"></sup>the mystery hidden for ages and generations but now revealed to his saints.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29476BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29476BS\"></sup>To them God chose to make known how great among the Gentiles are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29476BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29476BT\"></sup>the riches of the glory of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29476BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29476BU\"></sup>this mystery, which is Christ in you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29476BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29476BV\"></sup>the hope of glory.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Him we proclaim, warning everyone and teaching everyone with all wisdom, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29477BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29477BW\"></sup>we may present everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29477BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29477BX\"></sup>mature in Christ.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29478BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29478BY\"></sup>I toil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29478BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29478BZ\"></sup>struggling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29478CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29478CA\"></sup>with all his energy that he powerfully works within me."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>For I want you to know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29479A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29479A\"></sup>how great a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29479B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29479B\"></sup>struggle I have for you and for those at Laodicea and for all who have not seen me face to face,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29480C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29480C\"></sup>their hearts may be encouraged, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29480D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29480D\"></sup>knit together in love, to reach all the riches of full assurance of understanding and the knowledge of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29480E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29480E\"></sup>God's mystery, which is Christ,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29481F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29481F\"></sup>in whom are hidden all the treasures of wisdom and knowledge.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I say this in order <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29482G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29482G\"></sup>that no one may delude you with plausible arguments.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29483H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29483H\"></sup>though I am absent in body, yet I am with you in spirit, rejoicing to see your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29483I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29483I\"></sup>good order and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29483J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29483J\"></sup>the firmness of your faith in Christ.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29484K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29484K\"></sup>Therefore, as you received Christ Jesus the Lord, so walk in him,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29485L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29485L\"></sup>rooted and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29485M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29485M\"></sup>built up in him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29485N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29485N\"></sup>established in the faith, just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29485O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29485O\"></sup>as you were taught, abounding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29485P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29485P\"></sup>in thanksgiving.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>See to it that no one takes you captive by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29486Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29486Q\"></sup>philosophy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29486R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29486R\"></sup>empty deceit, according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29486S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29486S\"></sup>human tradition, according to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29486T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29486T\"></sup>elemental spirits of the world, and not according to Christ.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29487U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29487U\"></sup>in him the whole fullness of deity dwells <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29487V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29487V\"></sup>bodily,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29488W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29488W\"></sup>you have been filled in him, who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29488X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29488X\"></sup>the head of all rule and authority.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In him also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29489Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29489Y\"></sup>you were circumcised with a circumcision made without hands, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29489Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29489Z\"></sup>putting off the body of the flesh, by the circumcision of Christ,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29490AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29490AA\"></sup>having been buried with him in baptism, in which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29490AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29490AB\"></sup>you were also raised with him through faith in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29490AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29490AC\"></sup>the powerful working of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29490AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29490AD\"></sup>who raised him from the dead.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29491AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29491AE\"></sup>And you, who were dead in your trespasses and the uncircumcision of your flesh, God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29491AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29491AF\"></sup>made alive together with him, having forgiven us all our trespasses,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29492AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29492AG\"></sup>canceling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29492AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29492AH\"></sup>the record of debt that stood against us with its legal demands. This he set aside, nailing it to the cross.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29493AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29493AI\"></sup>He disarmed the rulers and authorities and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29493AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29493AJ\"></sup>put them to open shame, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29493AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29493AK\"></sup>triumphing over them in him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore let no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29494AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29494AL\"></sup>pass judgment on you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29494AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29494AM\"></sup>in questions of food and drink, or with regard to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29494AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29494AN\"></sup>a festival or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29494AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29494AO\"></sup>a new moon or a Sabbath.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29495AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29495AP\"></sup>These are a shadow of the things to come, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29495AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29495AQ\"></sup>the substance belongs to Christ.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Let no one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29496AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29496AR\"></sup>disqualify you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29496AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29496AS\"></sup>insisting on asceticism and worship of angels, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29496AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29496AT\"></sup>going on in detail about visions, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29496AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29496AU\"></sup>puffed up without reason by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29496AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29496AV\"></sup>his sensuous mind,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29497AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29497AW\"></sup>not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29497AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29497AX\"></sup>holding fast to the Head, from whom the whole body, nourished and knit together through its joints and ligaments, grows with a growth that is from God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>If with Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29498AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29498AY\"></sup>you died to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29498AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29498AZ\"></sup>elemental spirits of the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29498BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29498BA\"></sup>why, as if you were still alive in the world, do you submit to regulations—",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29499BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29499BB\"></sup>“Do not handle, Do not taste, Do not touch”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>(<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29500BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29500BC\"></sup>referring to things that all perish as they are used)—according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29500BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29500BD\"></sup>human precepts and teachings?",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>These have indeed an appearance of wisdom in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29501BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29501BE\"></sup>promoting self-made religion and asceticism and severity to the body, but they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29501BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29501BF\"></sup>of no value in stopping the indulgence of the flesh."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29502A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29502A\"></sup>If then you have been raised with Christ, seek <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29502B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29502B\"></sup>the things that are above, where Christ is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29502C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29502C\"></sup>seated at the right hand of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29503D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29503D\"></sup>Set your minds on things that are above, not on things that are on earth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29504E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29504E\"></sup>you have died, and your life is hidden with Christ in God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29505F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29505F\"></sup>who is your life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29505G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29505G\"></sup>appears, then you also will appear with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29505H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29505H\"></sup>in glory.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29506I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29506I\"></sup>Put to death therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29506J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29506J\"></sup>what is earthly in you: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29506K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29506K\"></sup>sexual immorality, impurity, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29506L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29506L\"></sup>passion, evil desire, and covetousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29506M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29506M\"></sup>which is idolatry.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29507N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29507N\"></sup>On account of these the wrath of God is coming.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29508O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29508O\"></sup>In these you too once walked, when you were living in them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29509P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29509P\"></sup>you must put them all away: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29509Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29509Q\"></sup>anger, wrath, malice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29509R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29509R\"></sup>slander, and obscene talk from your mouth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29510S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29510S\"></sup>Do not lie to one another, seeing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29510T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29510T\"></sup>you have put off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29510U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29510U\"></sup>the old self with its practices",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29511V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29511V\"></sup>have put on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29511W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29511W\"></sup>the new self, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29511X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29511X\"></sup>which is being renewed in knowledge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29511Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29511Y\"></sup>after the image of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29511Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29511Z\"></sup>its creator.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29512AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29512AA\"></sup>Here there is not Greek and Jew, circumcised and uncircumcised, barbarian, Scythian, slave, free; but Christ is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29512AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29512AB\"></sup>all, and in all.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29513AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29513AC\"></sup>Put on then, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29513AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29513AD\"></sup>God's chosen ones, holy and beloved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29513AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29513AE\"></sup>compassionate hearts, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29513AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29513AF\"></sup>kindness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29513AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29513AG\"></sup>humility, meekness, and patience,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29514AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29514AH\"></sup>bearing with one another and, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29514AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29514AI\"></sup>if one has a complaint against another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29514AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29514AJ\"></sup>forgiving each other; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29514AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29514AK\"></sup>as the Lord has forgiven you, so you also must forgive.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And above all these put on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29515AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29515AL\"></sup>love, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29515AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29515AM\"></sup>binds everything together in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29515AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29515AN\"></sup>perfect harmony.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29516AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29516AO\"></sup>the peace of Christ rule in your hearts, to which indeed you were called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29516AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29516AP\"></sup>in one body. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29516AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29516AQ\"></sup>be thankful.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29517AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29517AR\"></sup>the word of Christ dwell in you richly, teaching and admonishing one another in all wisdom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29517AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29517AS\"></sup>singing psalms and hymns and spiritual songs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29517AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29517AT\"></sup>with thankfulness in your hearts to God.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29518AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29518AU\"></sup>whatever you do, in word or deed, do everything in the name of the Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29518AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29518AV\"></sup>giving thanks to God the Father through him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29519AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29519AW\"></sup>Wives, submit to your husbands, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29519AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29519AX\"></sup>is fitting in the Lord.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Husbands, love your wives, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29520AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29520AY\"></sup>do not be harsh with them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Children, obey your parents <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29521AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29521AZ\"></sup>in everything, for this pleases the Lord.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Fathers, do not provoke your children, lest they become discouraged.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Bondservants, obey <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29523BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29523BA\"></sup>in everything those who are your earthly masters, not by way of eye-service, as people-pleasers, but with sincerity of heart, fearing the Lord.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29524BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29524BB\"></sup>Whatever you do, work heartily, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29524BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29524BC\"></sup>as for the Lord and not for men,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>knowing that from the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29525BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29525BD\"></sup>you will receive the inheritance as your reward. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29525BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29525BE\"></sup>You are serving the Lord Christ.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For the wrongdoer will be paid back for the wrong he has done, and there is no partiality."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Masters, treat your bondservants justly and fairly, knowing that you also have a Master in heaven.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29528A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29528A\"></sup>Continue steadfastly in prayer, being watchful in it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29528B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29528B\"></sup>with thanksgiving.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>At the same time, pray also for us, that God may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29529C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29529C\"></sup>open to us a door for the word, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29529D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29529D\"></sup>to declare the mystery of Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29529E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29529E\"></sup>on account of which I am in prison—",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>that I may make it clear, which is how I ought to speak.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29531F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29531F\"></sup>Walk in wisdom toward <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29531G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29531G\"></sup>outsiders, making the best use of the time.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Let your speech always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29532H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29532H\"></sup>be gracious, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29532I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29532I\"></sup>seasoned with salt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29532J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29532J\"></sup>so that you may know how you ought to answer each person.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Tychicus will tell you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29533K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29533K\"></sup>all about my activities. He is a beloved brother and faithful minister and fellow servant in the Lord.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I have sent him to you for this very purpose, that you may know how we are and that he may encourage your hearts,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29535L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29535L\"></sup>Onesimus, our faithful and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29535M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29535M\"></sup>beloved brother, who is one of you. They will tell you of everything that has taken place here.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29536N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29536N\"></sup>Aristarchus my fellow prisoner greets you, and Mark <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29536O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29536O\"></sup>the cousin of Barnabas (concerning whom you have received instructions—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29536P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29536P\"></sup>if he comes to you, welcome him),",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and Jesus who is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29537Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29537Q\"></sup>Justus. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29537R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29537R\"></sup>These are the only men of the circumcision among my fellow workers for the kingdom of God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29537S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29537S\"></sup>they have been a comfort to me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29538T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29538T\"></sup>Epaphras, who is one of you, a servant of Christ Jesus, greets you, always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29538U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29538U\"></sup>struggling on your behalf in his prayers, that you may stand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29538V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29538V\"></sup>mature and fully assured in all the will of God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For I bear him witness that he has worked hard for you and for those in Laodicea and in Hierapolis.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29540W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29540W\"></sup>Luke the beloved physician greets you, as does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29540X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29540X\"></sup>Demas.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Give my greetings to the brothers at Laodicea, and to Nympha and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29541Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29541Y\"></sup>the church in her house.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29542Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29542Z\"></sup>this letter has been read among you, have it also read in the church of the Laodiceans; and see that you also read the letter from Laodicea.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And say to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29543AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29543AA\"></sup>Archippus, “See that you fulfill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29543AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29543AB\"></sup>the ministry that you have received in the Lord.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I, Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29544AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29544AC\"></sup>write this greeting with my own hand. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29544AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29544AD\"></sup>Remember <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29544AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29544AE\"></sup>my chains. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29544AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29544AF\"></sup>Grace be with you."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;